DESCRIPTION:Still Got It Productions presents a three-show comedic whirlwin
 d exploring chaos\, confidence\, and unapologetic truth. we are the combina
 tion of 'Mischief and Mayhem' that crashes through next with joyful\, high-
 energy depictions of life's nonsense\, turning chaos into triumph. The Fina
 l Flourish brings the punchlines to a climax with our maximum comedic fire.
  Derya Yildirim - Prop-making\, chaos-powered comic turning trauma into gli
 ttering nonsense with the energy of an Ethnic Minority Bob the Builder on e
 spresso. Georgia Thorp - A master of deadpan humour who mines everything fr
 om the absurdity of everyday life to the sheer difficulty of\, well... exis
 ting. Courtney K Cornfield- A witty\, quirky observational musings of a mis
 fit Canadian single ND mum in a foreign land with a shrinking bank account\
 , growing waistline and certain the hot flashes are responsible for the ice
  caps melting.\nMore info: https://comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/still
 -got-it/
